description: Keep tests in a dedicated folder for each code section
globs: "**/*.test.ts"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Test organization

- Put tests in the nearest section's `test/` folder.
- Keep test filenames aligned with the source module: `feature.ts` uses `test/feature.test.ts`.
- Do not place `*.test.ts` files beside production source files.
- Use `convex/test/` for Convex tests.
